OL,3,CJersey government to cut civil service
OL,4,Cjobs in restructure review
OL,6,FSome Jersey civil servants will be
OL,7,Fmade redundant as part of the
OL,8,FGovernment's restructure.
OL,10,FIt is also freezing the recruitment of
OL,11,Fall new officials who would earn more
OL,12,Fthan #66,000.
OL,14,FThe announcements come as part of a
OL,15,Fnine-month review called the Common
OL,16,FStrategic Policy which looks at how
OL,17,Fthe Government can cut costs.
