OL,3,CJersey government to cut civil service
OL,4,Cjobs in restructure review
OL,6,FThe wider document sets out 13
OL,7,Fpriorities of the Council of Ministers
OL,8,Funtil the end of the current political
OL,9,Fterm in 2026.
OL,11,FIt outlines benefits for households,
OL,12,Ffamilies, patients and care providers,
OL,13,Fislanders, businesses and the
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,FITV News understands the measures will
OL,17,Fnot affect frontline workers such as
OL,18,Fnurses and doctors.
