OL,3,CJersey government to cut civil service
OL,4,Cjobs in restructure review
OL,6,FAs of today, grade 11 jobs and above -
OL,7,Fthat is people who earn #66,000 and
OL,8,Fmore - will no longer be advertised.
OL,10,FAny vacant positions that have been on
OL,11,Fthe books for more than six months
OL,12,Fwill now be taken down.
OL,14,FThis freeze is going to last for nine
OL,15,Fmonths because the Government says it
OL,16,Fdoesn't make sense to continue to
OL,17,Frecruit people when they are trying to
OL,18,Frestructure the Civil Service.
