OL,3,CJersey government to cut civil service
OL,4,Cjobs in restructure review
OL,6,FThey will be redeploying some staff
OL,7,Fbut ultimately they are hoping it is
OL,8,Fgoing to save them a lot of money.
OL,10,FAs part of that, some civil servants
OL,11,Fwill be made redundant.
OL,13,FDeputy Malcolm Ferey from the States
OL,14,FEmployment Board says: "Nine months is
OL,15,Fa long time to actually look at the
OL,16,Fstructure of the Civil Service to make
OL,17,Fsure we redeploy the people and if
OL,18,Fthere are any job losses, that they
OL,19,Fmake the way through the system.
