OL,3,CJersey government to cut civil service
OL,4,Cjobs in restructure review
OL,6,F"It is going to be a long piece of
OL,7,Fwork, it's not going to be easy but it
OL,8,Fwill be worth it when we get there."
OL,10,FThe size of the Communications
OL,11,FDepartment has been controversial.
OL,13,FTo put it into perspective, as of
OL,14,FSeptember 2023, 34 people were working
OL,15,Fin the team costing millions of pounds.
OL,17,FIn comparison, the States of Guernsey
OL,18,Fonly has nine members of comms staff
OL,19,Fand there are just eight in the Isle
OL,20,Fof Man Government.
