OL,3,CJersey government to cut civil service
OL,4,Cjobs in restructure review
OL,6,FThere have been questions raised
OL,7,Fbefore about whether somewhere like
OL,8,FJersey. with only 100,000 people,
OL,9,Fneeds a team that big.
OL,11,FNow we are hearing that the Government
OL,12,Fis looking to make around a third of
OL,13,Fits comms team redundant and they're
OL,14,Fcurrently in a consultation period.
OL,16,FIt is an uncertain time for many civil
OL,17,Fservants and when the new Government
OL,18,Fbuilding opens in a matter of weeks,
OL,19,Fmany may be concerned about their
OL,20,Ffuture.
